Installation:

Assumes the CATALINA_HOME environmental variable is set to the home of your TOMCAT install

[user@server thredds-styles]$ git clone git://github.com/asascience-open/thredds-styles.git
[user@server thredds-styles]$ cd thredds-styles
[user@server thredds-styles]$ cp -r images folder.gif tds.css tdsCat.css $CATALINA_HOME/webapps/thredds/


Development:

The meta.html and tree.html files provide static HTML for typical THREDDS webpages.  Use these as templates when changing the CSS and images.